cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM 

The paper deals with image-to-image translation using GANs, which is a popular topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The proposed method involves attention mechanisms, which are commonly used in deep learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the limitations of existing models and proposes a novel approach, which could fall under the graphics (cs.GR) or multimedia (cs.MM) categories.
